thread.title: Steelers rally behind backup Jones, stun Cardinals 25-13

title: Steelers rally behind backup Jones, stun Cardinals 25-13
text:
> Pennsylvania Steelers rally behind backup Jones, stun Cardinals 25-13 Pittsburgh Steelers quarterback Landry Jones (3) celebrates with tight end Matt Spaeth (89) after throwing a touchdown pass to wide receiver Martavis Bryant in the fourth quarter an NFL football game against the Arizona Cardinals, Sunday, Oct. 18, 2015 in Pittsburgh. The Steelers won 25-13. (AP Photo/Gene J. Puskar) The most compelling, sharable stories from across the web.
